ting Mn de-wetting. This study unravels the details of Mn-Ge\ninteractions, and demonstrates the role of surface diffusion as a determinant\nin the growth of Mn-doped Ge materials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Oct 2012 22:04:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-10-31"}
