pecial attention is paid to the\nevolution towards chiral restoration, as well as to the comparison with recent\nlattice analysis.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Oct 2012 12:18:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 5 Jan 2013 22:39:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-01-08"}
